To use tripwire to protect your systems, you should first initialise
the databases:

	(cd ${PREFIX}/etc/tripwire; ${PREFIX}/sbin/tripwire -initialize)

which creates the database in the ${PREFIX}/etc/tripwire/databases
directory.

===========================================================================
